# 🚀 AI-Powered OCR Autofill Browser Extension

An AI-powered browser extension that extracts information from scanned documents using OCR and intelligently autofills complex web forms using semantic field mapping.

The project combines:

* OCR (Optical Character Recognition)
* AI-assisted semantic matching
* Dynamic DOM analysis
* Browser automation
* Intelligent form autofill

---

# ✨ Features

## 📄 Intelligent Document Extraction

Supports multiple document formats:

* Images (`png`, `jpg`, `jpeg`, `webp`)
* PDFs
* DOCX
* XLSX
* PPTX
* TXT / CSV / HTML files
* Handwritten documents

The system extracts and understands:

* Names
* Addresses
* Phone numbers
* Emails
* DOB
* Student IDs
* Branch/Course details
* Contextual labels
* Handwritten text
* Document structure
* Other meaningful information present in the document

---

## 🧠 AI-Assisted Semantic Mapping

Instead of relying only on hardcoded selectors or exact field names, the system uses semantic matching.

Example:

```text
Roll Number → Student ID
Father Name → Parent Name
```

Even when wording differs, the extension intelligently maps fields based on contextual meaning.

---

# 🌐 Dynamic Form Understanding

The browser extension analyzes:

* Labels
* Placeholders
* Nearby text
* DOM structure
* iframe elements
* Shadow DOM components

This allows the extension to work across:

* Google Forms
* Dynamic multi-step portals
* React-based forms
* Public-service style workflows
* Complex modern web applications

---

# ⚡ Smart Autofill Engine

Once fields are mapped:

* Inputs are filled automatically
* Native browser events are triggered
* Dynamic validations are handled properly
* React-controlled inputs are updated correctly

---

# 🛠 Tech Stack

## Frontend / Extension

* JavaScript
* Chrome Extension Manifest V3
* HTML / CSS

## Backend

* Python
* FastAPI

## OCR & AI

* OpenCV
* Tesseract OCR
* Gemini AI

